{
  "texts": [
    "Ekaputra et al. [3] gives a general overview of current research on the combination of the broad field of ML and semantic web.Searching Google Scholar and Semantic Scholar with \"knowledge graph ChatGPT\", \"ontology ChatGPT\" and \"rdf ChatGPT\" in the beginning of April 2023 results in only two relevant papers.",
    "The first one, [7], reviews the differences between conversational AI models, prominent ChatGPT, and state-of-the-art question-answering systems for knowledge graphs.",
    "In their survey and experiments, they detect capabilities of their used frameworks but highlight ChatG-PTs explainability and robustness.",
    "The second one, [6], discusses the usage of ChatGPT for database management tasks when tabular schema is expressed in a natural language.",
    "They conclude among others that ChatGPT is able to assist in complex semantic integration and table joins to simplify database management and enhance productivity."
  ]
}